## 📦 Installation Instructions

### 1. Initialize the Project

```bash
# Create project directory
mkdir videotube-frontend
cd videotube-frontend

# Copy all configuration files to root directory
# Copy src/ folder with all source files
# Copy tests/ folder with all test files

# Install dependencies
npm install
```

### 2. Set Up Environment Variables

```bash
# Copy the example environment file
cp .env.example .env

# Edit .env with your values (can use defaults for now)
```

### 3. Verify Installation

```bash
# Check TypeScript compilation
npm run type-check

# Should output: "No errors found"
```

---

## 🧪 Testing Phase 2.1

### Run All Tests

```bash
# Run all unit tests
npm run test

# Expected output:
# ✓ tests/unit/lib/mockData.test.ts (XX tests passing)
# ✓ tests/unit/config/branding.test.ts (XX tests passing)
# 
# Test Files  2 passed (2)
# Tests  XX passed (XX)
```

### Run Tests with Coverage

```bash
npm run test:coverage

# Expected minimum coverage:
# Statements   : 80% ( XX/XX )
# Branches     : 75% ( XX/XX )
# Functions    : 80% ( XX/XX )
# Lines        : 80% ( XX/XX )
```

### Run Tests in Watch Mode

```bash
npm run test:watch

# Tests will re-run automatically when files change
```

### Run Tests with UI

```bash
npm run test:ui

# Opens Vitest UI in browser at http://localhost:51204
```

